snippet.title: The Ultimatum: Choices | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Your relationship is on the line in this interactive fiction game based on the hit series. Are you ready to say "I do," or will you find someone new?

Play The Ultimatum: Choices on your mobile devices. Available exclusively on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/game/81763213

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with 283 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.
